======================================
========= GeeXboX libvahalla =========
====== A tiny media scanner API ======
======================================

Libvalhalla is a library written in C. It is a media scanner, that
stores various information in an SQLite database and relies on
FFmpeg (libavformat and libavutil) and libcurl. It features many
Internet grabbers that allows automatic download of covers, lyrics,
informations on media files, tags retrival in video and music files
and so on.

It is a free software - it is licensed under the terms of the
GNU Lesser General Public License (GNU/LGPL) version 2.1+.
